PBOC Adviser Zhou Qiren Says Inflation Remains Top Challenge

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-09-22T01:46:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/pboc-adviser-zhou-qiren-says-inflation-remains-top-challenge.html
Chinese central bank adviser Zhou
Qiren said consumer price gains haven’t shown signs of “easing
considerably” and that tackling inflation remains the nation’s
“No. 1 challenge.”  “We can’t take it lightly,” Zhou said at a conference in
the city of Changchun today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
